  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para>A <guilabel>Spacecraft</guilabel> resource is GMAT's spacecraft
    model and includes data and models for the spacecraft's orbit, epoch,
    attitude, and physical parameters (such as mass and drag coefficient), as
    well as attached hardware, including tanks and thrusters. The
    <guilabel>Spacecraft</guilabel> model also contains the data that
    configures how the <guilabel>Spacecraft</guilabel> 3-D CAD model is used
    in an <guilabel>OrbitView</guilabel>.</para>

    <para>GMAT's documentation for <guilabel>Spacecraft</guilabel> is
    extensive and is broken down into the following sections:</para>

